# Copy to: .github/CODEOWNERS (repository root)
# Replace @your-github-username with real users or @org/teams
# Docs: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# Default owner for everything (optional — remove if too noisy)
* @your-github-username

# Course lab: automation code
/lab2/** @your-github-username

# Pipeline definitions — often owned by DevOps
/.github/workflows/** @your-github-username
